Package com.twiddles.ganesha.gui

Provides classes for displaying the Ganesha application GUI and interacting with the user.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ObjectTable Interface for tables that hold RDF objects.
 

Class Summary
AddWizard Wizard interface to let users add new resources, properties or objects.
ContainerWindow A container editing window.
ContainerWindowListener ActionListener to control the exit behaviour of a Container window.
GDesktop The internal desktop area of the main Ganesha window.
GMenu The menubar for the main app window.
GToolbar The toolbar for the main app window.
GUI The main application window of Ganesha.
GUIEvent ActionListener for various menu and toolbar items.
GUIWindowListener ActionListener to control the exit behaviour of Ganesha's main window.
HtmlLinker Dialog to let the user insert a link to the current RDFFile into an existing (X)HTML file.
ObjectEditor Functionality for editing values in an Object table.
ObjectRenderer Renderer for the value (ie object) column
RDFFileFilter RDF/XML file filter for the file choosing dialogs.
ResourceList The list of RDF resources for the main app window.
ResourceListEntry Container for the data that makes up an entry in the Resource list.
ResourceListEvent ActionListener for buttons on the resource list.
ResourceWindow A resource editing window.
ResourceWindowListener ActionListener to control the exit behaviour of a Resource window.
SkinEvent ActionListener to switch the GUI's look and feel.
SplashScreen The Ganesha splash screen.
